Recipes List View Application

This is a single-page application that showcases a list of recipes. It follows Clean Architecture,
uses MVVM pattern, coroutines Flow, Hilt, and viewBinding.

Justifications:
Clean Architecture: Separation of concerns, maintainability, testability.
MVVM Pattern: Clear separation of UI and business logic, reusability, testability.
Coroutines Flow: Asynchronous operations, reactive UI updates.
ViewBinding: Improved view binding, code readability.
Hilt: Simplified dependency injection.

Testing Strategies:
Unit Testing: Test ViewModel, Repository, and DataSource in isolation.
Integration Testing: Verify interaction between different layers.
UI Testing: Test UI behavior, interactions, and edge cases.